{
  "stem": "2133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Berehovo, Beregszasz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in-- under the German occupation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What kind of a rules?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, we weren't able-- we weren't allowed to go outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We weren't allowed to just freely, you know, go around the city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was-- there were curfews for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I was always an idealistic child, and I always believed on everybody's freedom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very difficult to understand why, just because being Jewish, you have to endure all that kind of a treatment from-- from people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I have to admit that I wish I could, you know, say that there was-- they were very supportive, but they weren't.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They turned their cheek on the other way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They weren't very nice, most of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no answer, if I would ask them why, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I certainly did, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- it was very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were constantly living in fear what going to happen, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even that we heard from some people that they're going to take us to Germany to work and-- and to the camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had absolutely no understanding what that really truly meant, you know, about what our future going to be.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't look good, but we didn't believe that, in the 20th century, when-- when the human race supposed to be on-- on on the top, far as intelligent concern, and to-- or-- and still to have such a brutal treatment toward another human being.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That it's possible to be, you know, in the 20th century.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On-- on-- on my chest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't walk around without it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
